OL,4,CWorking from home job adverts rise
OL,5, There has been a rise in jobs that
OL,6, advertise working from home compared
OL,7, with before the Covid pandemic,
OL,8, recruitment firm Reed has told the BBC.
OL,10,FPrior to the pandemic, 1% of
OL,11,Frecruitment firm Reed's job vacancies
OL,12,Fadvertised remote working, but this
OL,13,Frose to 5% in 2021.
OL,15,FMany office workers shifted to flexible
OL,16,Fworking during coronavirus lockdowns.
OL,18,FReed said applications for jobs with
OL,19,Fremote working shot up, and outpaced
OL,20,Fthe number of vacancies.
